在[[義和團事件|義和團事件]]時，剽悍的[[甘軍|甘軍]]震撼[[德意志帝国|德意志帝国]]皇帝[[威廉二世_(德國)|威廉二世]]。他請求當時的「[[哈里發|哈里發]]，─ 鄂圖曼帝國蘇丹[[阿卜杜勒-哈米德二世|阿卜杜勒-哈米德二世]]依其哈里發名義想辦法讓同樣是穆斯林組成的甘軍停止戰鬥。哈米德二世同意威廉二世的請求，並讓恩維爾帕夏（「並非」是青年土耳其黨領袖的那位 [[恩維爾帕夏|恩維爾帕夏]]）在1901年抵達中國，但義和團事件早已平息。<ref>{{cite book|url=https://books.google.com/books?id=PvVlS3ljx20C&pg=PA237|title=The politicization of Islam: reconstructing identity, state, faith, and community in the late Ottoman state|author=Kemal H. Karpat|year=2001|publisher=Oxford University Press US|page=237|isbn=0-19-513618-7|access-date=2017-07-21|archive-date=2017-01-09|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170109134834/https://books.google.com/books?id=PvVlS3ljx20C&pg=PA237|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite book|title=China Considers the Middle East|issue=|volume=|first1=Lillian Craig|last1=Harris|year=1993|edition=illustrated|publisher=I. B. Tauris|url=https://books.google.com/books?id=fmptAAAAMAAJ&q=enver+pasha+kansu+concerned&dq=enver+pasha+kansu+concerned|page=56|isbn=1850435987|accessdate=1 April 2013|ref={{harvid||}}|archive-date=2017-01-09|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170109093044/https://books.google.com/books?id=fmptAAAAMAAJ&q=enver+pasha+kansu+concerned&dq=enver+pasha+kansu+concerned|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite book|title=The Moslem World, Volumes 1-3|issue=|volume=|first1=|last1=|others=Contributor Hartford Seminary Foundation|year=1966|edition=|publisher=Hartford Seminary Foundation|isbn=|url=https://books.google.com/books?id=xoJCAAAAYAAJ&dq=the+mysterious+mission+of+Enver+Pasha+to+Peking+at+the+outbreak+of+the+Boxer+Rebellion+and+his+alleged+conversation+with+Rustem+Pasha.%27+%27+At+the+time+of+the+Boxer+Rebellion%2C+the+Turkish+warship+%22+Ertogrul+%22appeared+in+Far+Eastern+waters+as&q=mysterious+Enver+Pasha|page=190|accessdate=1 April 2013|ref={{harvid||}}|archive-date=2017-01-09|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170109090046/https://books.google.com/books?id=xoJCAAAAYAAJ&dq=the+mysterious+mission+of+Enver+Pasha+to+Peking+at+the+outbreak+o