er-2014_-answer-of-the-spokesman-of-the-ministry-of-foreign-affairs-tanju-bilgi%C3%A7-in-to-a-question-regarding-the-life-imprisonment-sentence-against-uighur-scholar-ilham-tohti-on-a-charge-of-separatism.en.mfa |date=20160305010316 }}, Republic of Turkey Ministry of Foreign Affairs, 25 September 2014</ref>11月，土耳其外交部長表示願提供約300名自稱[[土耳其人|土耳其人]]的[[維吾爾人|維吾爾人]][[政治庇護|政治庇護]]，將這些人從所滯留的泰國帶到土耳其。<ref>[http://www.ntdtv.com/xtr/b5/2014/11/28/a1157377.html 300維吾爾逃至泰國被拘 土伸援手願庇護] {{Wayback|url=http://www.ntdtv.com/xtr/b5/2014/11/28/a1157377.html |date=20141229021604 }}, [[新唐人電視台|新唐人電視台]], 2014-11-27</ref><ref>[http://www.uyghurcongress.org/en/?p=24519 Turkey moves to help 300 Uighurs in Thailand] {{Wayback|url=http://www.uyghurcongress.org/en/?p=24519 |date=20141229023355 }}, World Uyghur Congress, 25 November 2014</ref><ref name="民報"/>

